# Trip-Scribe Technology Stack

## Core Framework

### Next.js 15.3.4 ⚠️ MAJOR UPDATE
- **App Router**: Using the new app directory structure
- **Server Components**: Default to server components for better performance
- **API Routes**: RESTful API endpoints in `/app/api/`
- **TypeScript**: Full TypeScript support with strict mode
- **Breaking Changes**: Major update from 13.5.4 to 15.3.4

**Best Practices:**
- Use Server Components by default, only add `'use client'` when necessary
- Implement proper loading states with `loading.tsx`
- Use error boundaries with `error.tsx`
- Leverage Next.js Image component for optimization
- Review Next.js 15 migration guide for breaking changes

